---
// Αρχείο: src/components/Contact.astro
---

<section id="contact" class="py-24 bg-dotted">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
            
            <div>
                <span class="eyebrow">Επικοινωνία</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2 mb-6">
                    Ας συζητήσουμε το έργο σας
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg mb-12">
                    Είτε είστε ιδιώτης που ξεκινάει τώρα, είτε αρχιτέκτονας που αναζητά συνεργάτη, είμαστε εδώ για να βρούμε τη λύση.
                </p>

                <div class="space-y-8">
                    
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="p-3 bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 rounded-lg shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 0 1-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 4.5v2.25Z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Τηλέφωνο</h3>
                            <a href="tel:+302102200607" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors text-lg font-medium block mt-1">
                                210 220 0607
                            </a>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Δευτέρα - Παρασκευή, 09:00 - 17:00</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="p-3 bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 rounded-lg shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Email</h3>
                            <a href="mailto:info@smarthomepro.gr" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors block mt-1">
                                info@smarthomepro.gr
                            </a>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Απαντάμε συνήθως εντός 24 ωρών.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="p-3 bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 rounded-lg shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Έδρα</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1">
                                Αττική, Ελλάδα
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Εξυπηρέτηση πανελλαδικά κατόπιν συνεννόησης.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
                <form
                    name="contact"
                    method="POST"
                    action="/efxaristoume/"
                    data-netlify="true"
                    netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
                    class="space-y-6"
                >
                    <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
                    <p class="hidden">
                        <label>Μην συμπληρώνετε αυτό το πεδίο: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div>
                            <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Ονοματεπώνυμο</label>
                            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 focus:border-teal-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-200 outline-none transition-all" placeholder="π.χ. Γιώργος Παπαδόπουλος" />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Τηλέφωνο</label>
                            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 focus:border-teal-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-200 outline-none transition-all" placeholder="π.χ. 6900000000" />
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Email</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 focus:border-teal-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-200 outline-none transition-all" placeholder="name@company.com" />
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="type" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Ενδιαφέρομαι για</label>
                        <select id="type" name="type" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 focus:border-teal-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-200 outline-none transition-all bg-white">
                            <option>Νέα εγκατάσταση KNX (Κατοικία)</option>
                            <option>Ξενοδοχειακή λύση</option>
                            <option>Συνεργασία (Αρχιτέκτονας/Μηχανικός)</option>
                            <option>Τεχνική Υποστήριξη</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Μήνυμα</label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 focus:border-teal-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-200 outline-none transition-all" placeholder="Περιγράψτε μας σύντομα τις ανάγκες σας..."></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-lg hover:from-emerald-400 hover:to-teal-500 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-teal-600/20">
                        Αποστολή Μηνύματος
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>